I didn’t expect to fall in love so deeply the first time I met you, but somehow, you charmed me with the sweetest smile I’ve ever seen. Little did I know, you would become the light in my darkness.

I’ve been to some of the darkest places, I messed up a lot, but I never lost faith in myself because, deep down inside, I knew I could do better. For the past two years, I fought demons every single day to become a better person. I stood alone, fighting those who wanted to drown me with my past and my pain. I became stronger than ever and overcame my trauma, and that's when I met you.

I was scared, but that didn’t stop me from showing you who I am. Yet, you still loved me in all my damaged glory. Even in the toughest times when no one believed my words, you stood right by my side, along with my friends and family, making me believe that everything was gonna be alright. After all I’ve been through, I’m finally blessed with the kindest, sweetest, and smartest man ever.

You motivate me, strengthen my beliefs, and teach me what love truly is. One day apart from you feels like a decade. Now, my mind is free from all the judgments and drama; the only thing I wanna focus on is a better future for both of us.

Happy 1-year anniversary @Alan Le 🥳
